                java.util.Collection<TerrainTile> tiles)
        Description copied from class: TerrainRenderService
        Obtains the terrain tiles to be rendered for the scene. The tiles are locked, and the mesh data is not eligible for deletion until they are unlocked via TerrainRenderService.unlock(Collection)
        Specified by:
        lock in class TerrainRenderService
        Parameters:
        view - The current scene. If null is specified, the the tiles returned from the last call to TerrainRenderService.lock(GLMapView, Collection) will be returned.
        tiles - The terrain tiles
        Returns:
